Kafka Topic
   ↓
KafkaEventConsumer
   ↓
EventRecordMapper (parses JSON → EventRecord)
   ↓
EventNotifierPort (InMemoryEventBus)
   ↓
ResumeEngine.accept(EventRecord)
   ↓
EventStoragePort.saveEvent/saveTestContext
   ↓
test_context.resumeReady = true
   ↓
CucumberTestRunner retries ONLY that scenario
